t more about your Website Design solution\">Increase your unique online presence, find out more about your Website Design solution</a></p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,688,'Main Full Area','<center>\r\n<h3 class=\"colour-grey\"><strong>With knowledge and commitment.</strong> For the best and most trusted services in the industry.</h3>\r\n</center>\r\n\r\n<center><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2015/0528/8907/logo-microsoft-azure.jpg\" alt=\"Microsoft Azure\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.pingdom.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2915/0528/8908/logo-pingdom.jpg\" alt=\"Pingdom\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://chriswatterston.ongooglesolutions.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/1515/0528/8909/icon-gsuite.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://freshdesk.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2415/0528/8907/icon-freshdesk.jpg\" alt=\"Freshdesk\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"http://www.concrete5.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/8815/0528/8906/logo-conrete5.jpg\" alt=\"Conrete5\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/analytics/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9215/0528/8909/icon-googleanalytics.jpg\" alt=\"Google Analytics\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/?ref=chris-watterston\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9315/0529/0056/icon-shopify.jpg\" alt=\"Shopify\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a></center>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,698,'Main Full Area','<hr/>',1668703382),(159,76,720,'Main eCommerce Area : 40','<p class=\"colour-white\">Your online store should be your store. With Shopify and a bespoke designed solution, your brand will be present from the core and beyond - something that doesn&#39;t come straight out the box.</p>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,721,'Main eCommerce Area : 41','<p class=\"colour-white\">Manage your entire inventory. Track stock counts, and automatically stop selling products when inventory runs out.&nbsp;There&#39;s no limit to the number or type of products you can sell in your online store.</p>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,722,'Main eCommerce Area : 42','<p class=\"colour-white\">Capture payments and fulfill your orders right from your phone. Send shipping notifications from the post office. Quickly see items that need your attention, and track trends as they happen in your store.</p>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,723,'Main eCommerce Area : 43','<p class=\"colour-white\">And the list goes on... <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/design-development-solutions-and-services/shopify-ecommerce-website-designer-solution\" title=\"Find out more about your eCommerce Design solution\">Find out more!</a></p>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,724,'Main Mobile App Area : 44','<p class=\"colour-white\">Your app is built using the latest of OS languages, resulting in great stability and reliability on every level. This also ensures a future proofed foundation, combined with the latest frameworks.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,725,'Main Mobile App Area : 45','<p class=\"colour-white\">Every mobile application I design and develop is created from the ground up, with your every need in mind. I believe in a unique product for every service provided to my clients - it&rsquo;s something I live by.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,726,'Main Mobile App Area : 46','<p class=\"colour-white\">Similar to that of the web, I integrate Google Analytics into your app. This allows you to view reports of user numbers, UI uses, what users enjoy accessing and read - all within your mobile application.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,727,'Main Mobile App Area : 47','<p class=\"colour-white\">And the list goes on... <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/design-development-solutions-and-services/mobile-app-designer-developer-solution\" title=\"Find out more about your Mobile Application solution\">Find out more!</a></p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,728,'Main Website Design Area : 48','<p class=\"colour-white\">Your website will be 100% responsive from the word go - promise. Built in the current mobile world, not 1998. Having to &quot;opt-in&quot; to receive responsive design shouldn&rsquo;t be required. Your website will look great on all desktop and mobile devices.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,729,'Main Website Design Area : 50','<p class=\"colour-white\">I always have you at heart, things shouldn&#39;t be harder than they need to be. That&#39;s why I have put years of trust into our CMS. It&#39;s ease of use and broad functionality makes it a true winner for all our clients.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,730,'Main Website Design Area : 51','<p class=\"colour-white\">And the list goes on... <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services/bespoke-website-designer-solution\" title=\"Find out more about website design solution\">Find out more!</a></p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,731,'Main Website Design Area : 49','<p class=\"colour-white\">I truly believe and follow that all websites, no matter what, should be accessible 24/7, 365 days of the year. I monitor every single one of your websites, making sure it is online - just like it should always be.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,777,'Title Content','<h2 class=\"colour-white\">Ensuring the online appearance of individuals, start-ups and established brands.</h2>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,778,'Title Content','<h1 class=\"colour-white\"><strong>I provide trusted solutions that will get you off the ground.</strong> Guaranteed.</h1>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,868,'Main General Area','<h1><strong>Can&#39;t find what you&#39;re looking for?</strong> Let&#39;s chat, don&#39;t be shy.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/index.php/design-development-solutions-and-services\" title=\"website, ecommerce and mobile app design solutions\">Have you seen my most common solutions?</a> I undertake many different request variations for my clients, from the smallest of things like a logo or icon design, right through to setting up their complete start-up branding or marketing campaign, involving multiple HTML email designs and creations - so that my client are only left to&nbsp;final check their content and click send.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>It may&nbsp;only take 5 minutes.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternitivly, let me can call you. Leave your details and I&#39;ll call you back within a few hours, or ASAP. <em>If in the very rare occurrence that we can&#39;t help, we may know a trusted person who can.</em></p>\r\n',1668703382),(159,76,916,'Main eCommerce Area','<p class=\"colour-white\">Your shop, your brand. I bring your eCommerce store to life and integrate into Shopify. Your online store should be your store. Shopify allows me to take years of experience, and apply a bespoke solution to your store. Applying a bespoke designed solution, your brand will be present from the core, and beyond - something that doesn&#39;t come straight out the box! Bespoke domain names, everything you need in one place, a unified platform to run your store.</p>\r\n',1668703380),(159,76,917,'Main Mobile App Area','<p class=\"colour-white\">There are already so many mobile applications on the market that are identical from one another, you want something unique, something branded - that&#39;s what I do. I listen to individuals, start-ups and brands, to uniquely help them prepare them for what hungry excitement lies ahead. From the collaborative planning, through to design, development, testing and launch. Let me create something beautiful for you and your audience.</p>\r\n',1668703381),(159,76,918,'Main Website Design Area','<p class=\"colour-white\">With the growing numbers of website on the internet, there are 100&#39;s, if not 1000&#39;s, of new comers during a month period. This means that the game gets harder with ev