a.org/wiki/Computer-aided_design\" target=\"_blank\">CAD</a> (Computer Aided Design).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was a need for us to take a level of control and ownership, to ensure areas didn&#39;t break or full behind. A full re-design and rebuild was actioned, with a clear messions that the visitor should feel that they have known CD Surveys Ltd for years. A blog was introduced, including more simplified copy and intuitive imagry.</p>\r\n',1668759288),(198,13,232,'Main Body Two','\n  <script>\n  $(document).ready(function(){\n      $(function () {\n          $(\"#ccm-image-slider-232\").responsiveSlides({\n              prevText: \"\",   // String: Text for the \"previous\" button\n              nextText: \"\",\n  		  		nav:true,\n  		pager: true,\n  		              timeout: 4000,              speed: 500,                                                    });\n      });\n  });\n  </script>\n\n  <div class=\"casestudy-slider ccm-image-slider-container ccm-block-image-slider-pages\" >\n      <div class=\"ccm-image-slider\">\n        <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-inner\">\n                      <ul class=\"rslides\" id=\"ccm-image-slider-232\">\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Jumping straight to the point</h3>\n                                        <p>We designed the websites homepage to tell&nbsp;the visitor their message instantly, providing them a service&nbsp;in which they require.</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/5814/9916/8291/cd-surveys-ltd-homepage-website-design.jpg\" alt=\"Jumping straight to the point\" width=\"1441\" height=\"1137\">                </li>\n                          </ul>\n                  </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n\n',1668759288),(198,13,873,'Main Body Three','<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We feel that this project has