">\n    <ul class=\"list-inline\">\n            <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/chriswatterston\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitter\"></i></a></li>\n            <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chriswatterston.co\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\"></i></a></li>\n            <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chriswatterston/\"><i class=\"fa fa-instagram\"></i></a></li>\n            <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/chriswatterston\"><i class=\"fa fa-github-square\"></i></a></li>\n        </ul>\n</div>\n	</div>\n</nav>\n',1513238899),(199,7,169,'Main','<hr/>',1668705172),(199,7,876,'Main','<h2>Interested in starting something together?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>I love meeting new people hearing what they want to achieve. Let&#39;s chat about what we can build together.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn orange\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/get-in-contact\" title=\"contact, get started today\">Get started today</a></p>\r\n',1668705172),(199,7,958,'Main','<p class=\"colour-white family-table\">Copyright &copy; 2017 Chris Watterston. All rights reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"colour-white family-table\"><a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/cookie-policy\" title=\"Cookie Policy\">Cookie Policy</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/terms-of-use\" title=\"Terms of Use\">Terms of Use</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/accessibility\" title=\"Accessibility\">Accessibility</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/shipping-returns-and-refund-policy\" title=\"Store policy\">Store Policy</a></p>\r\n',1668705175),(199,7,1048,'Main Body','<h3>Project goal</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The across the board goal was to ensure that CD Surveys fleet of vans could be recognised as theirs, no questions. It would include their logo, colouring, real essential contact and finally their services. The design also naturally had to work on other vans if need be, effectively a future proof design.</p>\r\n',1668705169),(199,7,1049,'Main Body','<h3 id=\"focus-on-process-before-artifact\">Process&nbsp;and research&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I presented a few thought out ideas, which grew to what is todays design. To help CD Surveys Ltd visualise, I took a photograph of one of their new vehicles and &lsquo;Photoshopped&rsquo; how the final design would look like. This reassured CD Surveys Ltd in how the final outcome would be and feel, before progressing onto organisation of the application. Everything went perfectly smooth.</p>\r\n',1668705169),(199,7,1050,'Main Body Three','<h3>Lessons Learned</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>During the early stages of creating the design concepts, we learnt that simplicity on small vehicles can be massive - simple in design, but big in impression. Using the bold colours already present within the CD Surveys Ltd logo, really helped to portray this impression, effectively &ldquo;extending&rdquo; the logo through the vehicle body to give the feeling of a bigger logo than what is actually.</p>\r\n',1668705171),(199,7,1051,'Main Body Three','<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The project as a&nbsp;whole took approximately 2 months to complete, this was from CD Surveys Ltd first conversation with us, through to the vehicles being driven around. Projects like this can vary in project scale, but this was a small/medium project that I really enjoyed. Even more that I witnessed their previous fleet of poorly sign written vehicle move onto new owners. The CD Surveys Ltd team love their new vehicles, and so do I.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn black\" href=\"http://www.cdsurveys.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Find out more, visit their website\">Find out more, visit their website</a></p>\r\n',1668705171),(199,7,1052,'Main Body Three','\n\n    <hr/>\n\n\n    <h2>Interested in starting something together?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>I love meeting new people hearing what they want to achieve. Let&#39;s chat about what we can build together.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn orange\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/get-in-contact\" title=\"contact, get started today\">Get started today</a></p>\r\n\n',1668705172),(199,7,1054,'Main Body Two','\n  <script>\n  $(document).ready(function(){\n      $(function () {\n          $(\"#ccm-image-slider-1054\").responsiveSlides({\n              prevText: \"\",   // String: Text for the \"previous\" button\n              nextText: \"\",\n  		  		nav:true,\n  		pager: true,\n  		              timeout: 4000,              speed: 500,                            auto: false,                        });\n      });\n  });\n  </script>\n\n  <div class=\"casestudy-slider ccm-image-slider-container ccm-block-image-slider-pages\" >\n      <div class=\"ccm-image-slider\">\n        <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-inner\">\n                      <ul class=\"rslides\" id=\"ccm-image-slider-1054\">\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Van signwriting during digital design</h3>\n                                        <p>One of our goals was to ensure that the final design would be future proof and work on any van make and model, you can see that the very minor changes had to be done to reflect the design concept onto the much larger Transit Connect van.</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/2715/0606/7067/cdsurveysltd-van-artwork.jpg\" alt=\"Van signwriting during digital design\" width=\"1500\" height=\"678\">                </li>\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Photoshopped Van Concepts</h3>\n                                        <p>To help enable CD Surveys Ltd visualise the design, we took a few photos of one of the new van and put them through Photoshop to visually lay the design concept onto the van - it&#39;s amazing how real it actually looks! Also noticed a glimpse of the poor previous van / signwritting in the background.</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/8815/0606/7064/cdsurveysltd-photoshop-van-concept.jpg\" alt=\"Photoshopped Van Concepts\" width=\"1500\" height=\"555\">                </li>\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Finished, rear off-side</h3>\n                                        <p>The outcome was fantastic, driving back from the&nbsp;signwritten guys catching eyes. You can see how the design compliments the follow of the vans lights.&nbsp;</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/1015/0606/7065/cdsurveysltd-van-final-01.jpg\" alt=\"Finished, rear off-side\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\">                </li>\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Finished, front off-side</h3>\n                                        <p>Using only the &#39;needed&#39; points of contact onto the vans, there is no need to cram a list of every method you can contact CD Surveys Ltd.&nbsp;</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/1915/0606/7062/cdsurveysltd-van-final-02.jpg\" alt=\"Finished, front off-side\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\">                </li>\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">Finished, rear near-side</h3>\n                                        <p>Services listing are placed in a spot were they can be read without any distractions. Categories clear, with full service listing shown smaller but still readable.</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/9415/0606/7060/cdsurveysltd-van-final-03.jpg\" alt=\"Finished, rear near-side\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\">                </li>\n                          </ul>\n                  </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n\n',1668705170),(199,7,1055,'Main Body Three','<h3>Testimonial</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>We commissioned Chris Watterston and his design capabilities to create and add a &lsquo;stand out&rsquo; livery for our 4 new Ford vans.<br />\r\nI can honestly say the result was outstanding and is very eye catching&hellip; even on the roof&hellip;<br />\r\nDue to this excellent work we have subsequently commissioned Chris to undertake a review of our Web pages then he<br />\r\nmoved onto our business cards. Both again very stunning results.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nGreat chap, great business, great ideas&hellip;.. will certainly use Chris again and recommend him to all my colleagues</blockquote>\r\n',1668705171),(199,7,1057,'Main','<ul>\r\n	<li><a class=\"contact colour-white type-lowercase type-semibold family-table\" href=\"/designer-developer-solutions-and-services\" title=\"eCommerce, Website Designer and Mobile App solutions\">Become a Client</a></li>\r\n	<li><a class=\"contact colour-white type-lowercase type-semibold family-table\" href=\"/get-in-contact\" title=\"Enquire for eCommerce, Website Design and Mobile App solutions\">Let&rsquo;s Talk?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',1668705174),(199,7,1141,'Main Body Three','<div class=\"cols more-posts\">\n    		<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-1\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatters