 are selling &mdash; and which ones aren&#39;t.&nbsp;See where your visitors come from, and how they found your online store, exporting reports for further analysis.</p>\r\n',1668703384),(202,98,737,'Main Body Two : 31','<h3><strong style=\"color:#94C03C;\">Sell online and accept payments in-store with POS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>POS&nbsp;software makes it easy to swipe credit cards and take cash offline, in your store standing by your customers side.&nbsp;Your Shopify Payments account is set up in less than 5 minutes, letting you process your customers&rsquo; credit cards directly through Shopify.</p>\r\n',1668703385),(202,98,738,'Main Body Two : 32','<h3><strong style=\"color:#94C03C;\">Discount codes, coupons and gift cards</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Run sales and promotions by offering coupon codes that save customers money. Choose whether the discount is for money off, a percentage off, free shipping, etc.&nbsp;Your customers are able to purchase a gift card for someone from your store, or you can use gift cards as store credit.</p>\r\n',1668703385),(202,98,739,'Main Body Two : 33','<h3><strong style=\"color:#94C03C;\">Sell on Facebook and more with social media integration</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>All Shopify solutions include social media integration, such as Pinterest, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, and Tumblr.&nbsp;Your Facebook fans can browse your products and make a purchase without even leaving Facebook.</p>\r\n',1668703385),(202,98,740,'Main Body Two','<div>\r\n<h3><strong style=\"color:#94C03C;\">An eCommerce platform that is continuously growing, even&nbsp;if you can&#39;t see it. Regular updates, SSL security, 99.99% uptime&nbsp;and more...</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>With so many features, Shopify really doe hits the nail on the head. And here are a few more;</strong><br />\r\nFull blogging platform, free SSL certificate, automatic taxes, abandoned checkout recovery, customer accounts and profiles, refunds, email templates, product reviews, email marketing, import/export, multiple images, unlimited bandwidth,&nbsp;99.99% uptime and 24/7 monitoring, traffic/referral reports,&nbsp;export reports, email or call customers, dedicated support team, and the list goes on.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',1668703385),(202,98,921,'Main Body Two','<h2><strong>Your shop, your brand.</strong> I bring your eCommerce store to life and integrate into Shopify.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Your online store should be your store. Shopify allows me to take years of experience, and apply a bespoke solution to your store. Applying a bespoke designed solution, your brand will be present from the core, and beyond - something that doesn&#39;t come straight out the box! Bespoke domain names, everything you need in one place, a unified platform to run your store.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DID YOU KNOW - </strong>a&nbsp;study showed that 94% of users disTRUSTED a website because of the DESIGN made them uneasy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn shopify\" href=\"#ecommerce-form\" title=\"Enquiry about your Shopify eCommerce solution\"><strong>Build trust,</strong> Chat about your Shopify eCommerce project today.</a></p>\r\n',1668703384),(202,98,958,'Main','<p class=\"colour-white family-table\">Copyright &copy; 2017 Chris Watterston. All rights reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"colour-white family-table\"><a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/cookie-policy\" title=\"Cookie Policy\">Cookie Policy</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/terms-of-use\" title=\"Terms of Use\">Terms of Use</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a class=\"colour-white\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/accessibility\" title=\"Accessibility\">Accessibility</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/legal-documentation/shipping-returns-and-refund-policy\" title=\"Store policy\">Store Policy</a></p>\r\n',1668703385),(202,98,1057,'Main','<ul>\r\n	<li><a class=\"contact colour-white t