f the above as standard. Become unique and unlike your competitors, let&#39;s have a chat about it today.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1668703393),(211,115,688,'Main Body Two','<center>\r\n<h3 class=\"colour-grey\"><strong>With knowledge and commitment.</strong> For the best and most trusted services in the industry.</h3>\r\n</center>\r\n\r\n<center><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2015/0528/8907/logo-microsoft-azure.jpg\" alt=\"Microsoft Azure\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.pingdom.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2915/0528/8908/logo-pingdom.jpg\" alt=\"Pingdom\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://chriswatterston.ongooglesolutions.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/1515/0528/8909/icon-gsuite.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://freshdesk.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2415/0528/8907/icon-freshdesk.jpg\" alt=\"Freshdesk\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"http://www.concrete5.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/8815/0528/8906/logo-conrete5.jpg\" alt=\"Conrete5\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/analytics/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9215/0528/8909/icon-googleanalytics.jpg\" alt=\"Google Analytics\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/?ref=chris-watterston\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9315/0529/0056/icon-shopify.jpg\" alt=\"Shopify\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a></center>\r\n',1668703393),(211,115,691,'Main Body Two','\n\n    <center>\r\n<h3 class=\"colour-grey\"><strong>With knowledge and commitment.</strong> For the best and most trusted services in the industry.</h3>\r\n</center>\r\n\r\n<center><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2015/0528/8907/logo-microsoft-azure.jpg\" alt=\"Microsoft Azure\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.pingdom.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2915/0528/8908/logo-pingdom.jpg\" alt=\"Pingdom\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://chriswatterston.ongooglesolutions.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/1515/0528/8909/icon-gsuite.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://freshdesk.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/2415/0528/8907/icon-freshdesk.jpg\" alt=\"Freshdesk\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"http://www.concrete5.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/8815/0528/8906/logo-conrete5.jpg\" alt=\"Conrete5\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/analytics/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9215/0528/8909/icon-googleanalytics.jpg\" alt=\"Google Analytics\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a><a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/?ref=chris-watterston\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/application/files/9315/0529/0056/icon-shopify.jpg\" alt=\"Shopify\" width=\"160\" height=\"82\"></a></center>\r\n\n',1668703393),(211,115,692,'Main Body Two','<hr/>',1668703393),(211,115,758,'Main Body Two : 26','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Swift and Kotlin, always using the latest languages</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Your app is built using the latest of OS languages, resulting in great stability and reliability on every level. This also ensures a future proofed foundation, combined with the latest frameworks.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,759,'Main Body Two : 27','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Complete upfront app planning</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s key that we outline all desired functionality and features in place and &ldquo;down on paper&rdquo; before the app process begins. We&rsquo;ll meet and collaborate on the app as a whole before any design and development work.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,760,'Main Body Two : 28','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">100% bespoke design and unique functionality</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every mobile application I design and develop is created from the ground up, with your every need in mind. I believe in a unique product for every service provided to my clients - it&rsquo;s something I live by.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,761,'Main Body Two : 29','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Complete design introduction, collaboration and satisfaction</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We sit down and discuss your every requirement. &nbsp;After we have created your layout wireframe and initial design, we will introduce our thoughts, ideas, and continue on collaboration.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,762,'Main Body Two : 30','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Branding your App so it really is yours</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s important that your app is branded to your unique organisation. You should be able to strip your name and logo from your content and still have your users know exactly who&rsquo;s mobile app they are using.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,763,'Main Body Two : 31','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Publishing to App Stores, I&#39;ve got this</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Publishing an app can be a complicated process which can waste time and cause you a headache. They involve certificates and provisioning profiles. I&#39;ll set up the required accounts and get everything ready for you.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,764,'Main Body Two : 32','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Bespoke App CMS, you&#39;ll have control</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on your app requirements, I&#39;ll introduce a bespoke content management system (CMS) for your app. Enabling you to push content, notification and much more - all through to your app in live time.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,765,'Main Body Two : 33','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Keep track with integrated Analytics</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Similar to that of the web, I integrate Google Analytics into your app. This allows you to view reports of user numbers, UI uses, what users enjoy accessing and read - all within your mobile application.</p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,766,'Main Body Two : 34','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Accessibility friendly, throughout</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Most mobile OS&rsquo;s feature built-in accessibility features, accessibility APIs and much more - and I make sure I 100% support these without fail. Supporting EVERY app user!</p>\r\n',1668703393),(211,115,767,'Main Body Two : 35','<h3><strong class=\"colour-orange\">Get involved with Beta early access</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I love the beta testing stage. It&rsquo;s when your app really comes to life! When&nbsp;runnning beta tests, I&nbsp;can allow multiple users early access - which means even you can beta test, if you&rsquo;d like?</p>\r\n',1668703393),(211,115,943,'Main Body Two','<h2><strong>Your mobile app, launch it.</strong> Let&#39;s take it to your already mobile addicted audience.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are already so many mobile applications on the market that are identical from one another, you want something unique, something branded - that&#39;s what I do. I listen to individuals, start-ups and brands, to uniquely help them prepare them for what hungry excitement lies ahead. From the collaborative planning, through to design, development, testing and launch. Let me create something beautiful for you and your audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DID YOU KNOW - </strong>a&nbsp;study showed that the average user spends 67 hours a month browsing on their mobile device, with 90% of that time used within third-party installed&nbsp;applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn mobileapp\" href=\"#mobileapp-form\" title=\"Enquiry about your mobile application today\">Don&#39;t regret it, chat about your mobile application project today</a></p>\r\n',1668703392),(211,115,958,'Main','<p class=\"colour-white family-table\">Copyright &copy; 2017 Chris Watterston. All rights reserved.<