OUND BY THE AFOREMENTIONED STATEMENT.</p>\r\n',1669331924),(216,21,890,'Main Body Three','<hr/>',1669331924),(216,21,900,'Main Body Three','<h2><strong>By accepting a quotation, to which will then be invoiced, you are agreeing to our&nbsp;full terms and conditions stated above.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Before Chris Watterston can commence the proposed Services, the client is requested to complete and submit the following form agreement form. After completion, a confirmation will be emailed to both Client and Chris Watterston stating this Service agreement.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Agreement Concerns</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any concerns relating to anything outline within this agreement, please contact&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:hello@chriswatterston.com?subject=Agreement%20Concerns%20-%20Terms%20and%20Agreement\">hello@chriswatterston.com</a>&nbsp;with your concerns before submitting the agreement form below.</p>\r\n',1669331924),(216,21,907,'Main Body Two','<p>The following terms and conditions document is a legal agreement between &ldquo;Chris Watterston&rdquo; and &ldquo;Client&rdquo; for the purposes of design, development, management, optimisation, print or support &quot;Services&quot;. These Terms and Conditions set forth the provisions under which the Client may use the Services supplied.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Acceptance Of Work</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Quotation and, or proposals received by the recipient are valid for 14 days only, unless otherwise stated on the documentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">No contract of service exists between Chris Watterston and Client until Chris Watterston receives written confirmation from client agreeing to the quoted or proposed project, via email or postal only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Any other Services on the order, which have not been included in the quotation, proposal or invoice, do not form part of the contract. The Client agrees to check the 