;shelf, bit it will never be 110% unique and &quot;made&quot; for that person. It takes a careful&nbsp;thought process, knowing them personally&nbsp;and&nbsp;understanding what they love to enjoy and how they&#39;ll use the gift. We&nbsp;feel it couldn&#39;t of turned out any better - bringing a smile to John every time he lifts his pint of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.guinness.com/en-gb/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Guinness\">Guinness</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What do you think, leave a comment - have you seen something to inspire you?</strong></p>\r\n',1668751700),(223,2,972,'Main Body','<img src=\"/application/files/4415/0594/6757/john-lucas-60th-birthday-beermat.jpg\" alt=\"Unique Guinness beer mats\" width=\"1190\" height=\"900\" class=\"ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-972\" title=\"Unique Guinness beer mats\">',1668751700),(223,2,973,'Main Body','<img src=\"/application/files/7015/0594/6756/john-lucas-60th-birthday-beermat-pint.jpg\" alt=\"Unique Guinness beer mats\" width=\"1190\" height=\"900\" class=\"ccm-image-block img-responsive bID-973\" title=\"Unique Guinness beer mats\">',1668751700),(223,2,1057,'Main','<ul>\r\n	<li><a class=\"contact colour-white type-lowercase type-semibold family-table\" href=\"/designer-developer-solutions-and-services\" title=\"eCommerce, Website Designer and Mobile App solutions\">Become a Client</a></li>\r\n	<li><a class=\"contact colour-white type-lowercase type-semibold family-table\" href=\"/get-in-contact\" title=\"Enquire for eCommerce, Website Design and Mobile App solutions\">Let&rsquo;s Talk?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',1668751700),(223,2,1140,'Main Body','<div class=\"cols more-posts\">\n    		<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-1\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatterston.com/application/files/cache/61d41fdb214113769c07f4368b183948.jpg\');\"></div>\n			<div class=\"news-content-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"news-content\">\n                    	<h2 class=\"colour-grey type-sem