 you&rsquo;ll understand why I say that. But if you haven&rsquo;t, then I think you should make it one of your priorities to do so next year. But make sure you take clothes for all seasons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The footage I captured during our break, between the short and unexpected showers, were achieved with &ldquo;the sexiest drone that DJI ever designed&ldquo;, the <a href=\"https://www.dji.com/phantom-4\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"DJI Phantom 4\">DJI Phantom 4</a>. This was my first attempt in creating a trailer for anything, let alone a trailer of our short break. Yeh I could of improved it a lot and admittedly missed some opportunities to capture some unique footage, but this is how we learn. I look forward to creating something similar in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1668759245),(235,5,1140,'Main Body','<div class=\"cols more-posts\">\n    		<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-1\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatterston.com/application/files/cache/b82215d79e4d002fc94f46a566d9d4ca.jpg\');\"></div>\n			<div class=\"news-content-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"news-content\">\n                    	<h2 class=\"colour-grey type-semibold\">Heathside School&#039;s unique website design</h2>\n          					<p class=\"description colour-grey\">\n													Heathside School, in Weybridge, approached me for their complete website redesign and development. They had recently undertaken the rebrand of their school logo and colouring, and as a result now wanted to continue the brands&hellip;											</p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/case-studies/heathside-schools-unique-website-design\" target=\"_self\" title=\"Continue reading, Heathside School&#039;s unique website design\" class=\"hidden\"></a>\n		</div>\n			<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-2\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatterston.com/application/files/cache/c0a53e1750181cc2a437e87408ce6f