ntire process.&rdquo; - Network Manager</blockquote>\r\n',1668759165),(236,16,1139,'Main Body Three','\n\n    <hr/>\n\n\n    <h2>Interested in starting something together?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>I love meeting new people hearing what they want to achieve. Let&#39;s chat about what we can build together.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"abtn orange\" href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/get-in-contact\" title=\"contact, get started today\">Get started today</a></p>\r\n\n',1668759165),(236,16,1141,'Main Body Three','<div class=\"cols more-posts\">\n    		<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-1\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatterston.com/application/files/cache/82bea14e0a6d89488cb575b7e516fb01.jpg\');\"></div>\n			<div class=\"news-content-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"news-content\">\n                    	<h2 class=\"colour-grey type-semibold\">A much needed Spotify widget for the Notification Center</h2>\n          					<p class=\"description colour-grey\">\n													Since installing the new operating system, OS X Yosemite, like many I&#039;ve noticed a hell of a lot of new great features and design. But, being an every day MacBook user, I&#039;m finding some pretty cool, but some also pretty&hellip;											</p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/blog/a-much-needed-spotify-widget-for-the-notification-center\" target=\"_self\" title=\"Continue reading, A much needed Spotify widget for the Notification Center\" class=\"hidden\"></a>\n		</div>\n			<div class=\"col newsfeed-entry entry-2\">\n			<div class=\"news-img\" style=\"background-image:url(\'http://www.chriswatterston.com/application/files/cache/f4d21ac5243b1017e5512e978cec68ce.jpg\');\"></div>\n			<div class=\"news-content-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"news-content\">\n                    	<h2 class=\"colour-grey type-semibold\">Creating PFX Certificate Files and installing SSL Certificates on your Microsoft Azure Web App Service</h2>\n          					<p class=\"description colour-grey\">\n													If you don&rsquo;t know much about HTTPS, SSL, CSR, PFX, CRT, P7B and manage a Cloud Hosting Infrastructure, such as Azure, then you may find it confusing when asked to supply .pfx files to bind and secure your application. I&rsquo;ve&hellip;											</p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/blog/creating-pfx-certificate-files-and-installing-ssl-certificates-on-your-microsoft-azure-web-app-service\" target=\"_self\" title=\"Continue reading, Creating PFX Certificate Files and installing SSL Certificates on your Microsoft Azure Web App Service\" class=\"hidden\"></a>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n',1513306701),(236,16,1148,'Main Body Three : 65','<center>\r\n<h1>11.55%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bounce Rate Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1149,'Main Body Three : 66','<center>\r\n<h1>9.05%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Average Sessions Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759165),(236,16,1150,'Main Body Three : 61','<center>\r\n<h1>46.99%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Desktop Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>8,342</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>12,262</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1151,'Main Body Three : 62','<center>\r\n<h1>111.80%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Mobile Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>4,161</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>8,813</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1152,'Main Body Three : 63','<center>\r\n<h1>121.15%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tablet Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>1,010</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>2,274</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1153,'Main Body Three : 64','<center>\r\n<h1>44.54%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>New Users Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1161,'Main Body','<h3 id=\"focus-on-process-before-artifact\">Process&nbsp;and research&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Having previously been employed within the education&nbsp;sector for 5 years, and now continuing to work alongside helping them for a further 4 years, I understand that <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services\">brand consistency</a> doesn&rsquo;t always transpire throughout&nbsp;nurseries, schools, colleges or universities. It was my job&nbsp;to ensure that the brand of St Paul&rsquo;s is properly continued through their newly <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services/bespoke-website-designer-solution\">designed responsive website</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The project began by ensuring I knew why their&nbsp;previous&nbsp;outdated website was failing&nbsp;and understanding the vision for improvement. Working alongside the Network Manager and leadership team at St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College, we set about&nbsp;creating a strategy aligned with their brand&rsquo;s ambition and audience&rsquo;s desires.</p>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1162,'Main Body Two','\n  <script>\n  $(document).ready(function(){\n      $(function () {\n          $(\"#ccm-image-slider-1162\").responsiveSlides({\n              prevText: \"\",   // String: Text for the \"previous\" button\n              nextText: \"\",\n  		  		nav:true,\n  		pager: true,\n  		              timeout: 4000,              speed: 500,                            auto: false,                        });\n      });\n  });\n  </script>\n\n  <div class=\"casestudy-slider ccm-image-slider-container ccm-block-image-slider-pages\" >\n      <div class=\"ccm-image-slider\">\n        <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-inner\">\n                      <ul class=\"rslides\" id=\"ccm-image-slider-1162\">\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                          <h3 class=\"ccm-image-slider-title type-semibold\">St Paul\'s Catholic College new website homepage</h3>\n                                        <p>The homepage holds a strong presence and continuation of the St Paul&#39;s brand. The design was grown from the previous design, with a &quot;box&nbsp;and grid&quot; like theme as one of the most important aspects to carry forward.</p>\r\n                  </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/9915/0877/7683/stpaulscatholiccollege-website-01.jpg\" alt=\"St Paul\'s Catholic College new website homepage\" width=\"1879\" height=\"2016\">                </li>\n                              <li>\n                                    <div class=\"ccm-image-slider-text\">\n                                                          </div>\n                  <img src=\"/application/files/9915/0877/7681/stpaulscatholiccollege-website-02.jpg\" alt=\"slide\" width=\"1879\" height=\"2839\">                </li>\n                          </ul>\n                  </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n\n',1668759164),(236,16,1163,'Main Body Three','<h3>Lessons Learned</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Since relaunching their new website, there has been a steep and steady increase of visitors, mostly mobile, through&nbsp;to their new website. It&rsquo;s proven obvious&nbsp;that once visitors became apparent of the <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services/bespoke-website-designer-solution\">redesign and development</a> to support mobile responsiveness, more visitors felt comfortable clicking through and viewing on their mobile devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the relaunch&nbsp;approximately 5 months ago, the results are staggering on how much of an improvement a modern and responsive website has given. We&rsquo;ve split the time since relaunch&nbsp;down the middle and compared the two results side-by-side to see really how much difference compatibility support does make.</p>\r\n',1668759164),(236,16,1164,'Main Body Three','<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Providing such an individual and reliable web solution that supports the broad compatibilities which are truly needed within this day and age on the web, has been an absolute pleasure. Collaboratively working alongside St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College&nbsp;has enabled me to effectively &quot;slingshot&quot; their online presence back into motion, therefore allowing their in-house administrators to take back control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only have I provided the <a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services\">design and development of their website solution</a>, but also the continued hosting, support and monitoring of the solution. This again, has provided fantastic results&nbsp;such as&nbsp;99.9% website uptimes and 359ms average response rates, over the past 5 months.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No doubt&nbsp;there will be a guaranteed continuation of fantastic results to come in the near future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1668759165),(236,16,1165,'Main Body','<h3>Project goal</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.st-pauls.surrey.sch.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College</a> are an incredible group of talented individuals who have a passion to teach. With a proven track record&nbsp;of growing from strength to strength with every passing academic year, St Paul&rsquo;s was continuing to heighten themselves but unfortunately&nbsp;their online expectation was merely frozen in time. Their in-house website administration team were unable to swiftly update the content effortlessly on the limited original Microsoft SharePoint platform, and unable to enable parents, students and potential admissions to seamlessly visit and use their website on all possible devices. St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College understood that their website was falling behind and something needed to be done - quickly!</p>\r\n',1668759164),(237,3,47,'Main','<h1 class=\"colour-white type-semibold type-uppercase\">Contact.</h1>\r\n',1668705176),(237,3,51,'Main','<h1 class=\"colour-white type-semibold type-uppercase\">Instagram.</h1>\r\n',1668705176),(237,3,62,'Main','<ul class=\"nav\"><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">Home</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/designer-developer-solutions-and-services\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">Solutions</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/what-we-do\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">What I do</a></li><li class=\"nav-path-selected\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/blog\" target=\"_self\" class=\"nav-path-selected\">News</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/case-studies\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">Case Studies</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/store\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">Store</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.chriswatterston.com/get-in-contact\" target=\"_self\" class=\"\">Get in Contact</a></li></ul>',1513072482),(237,3,64,'Main','<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/application/themes/chriswatterston/js/instafeed.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n    var feed = new Instafeed({\n		    get: \'user\',\n		    limit: \'4\',\n		    userId: \'3422386301\',\n		    accessToken: \'3422386301.1677ed0.88235c51522143ba86647d6cabe7818c\',\n		    template:\'<a href={{link}} target=\"_blank\" title=\"Follow me to find out what im up to on Instagram\"><span>{{likes}}</span><img src={{image}} alt=\"\"/></a>\'\n    });\n    feed.run();\n</script>\n<div id=\"instafeed\"></div>\n',1668705177),(237,3,65,'Main','\n<div id=\"ccm-block-social-links65\" class=\"ccm-block-social-links\">\n    <ul class=\"list-inline\">\n            <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/chriswatterston\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitte