s forward, weve ensured nobody is being missed out.','/case-studies/saint-michael-primary-school-website-design','2016-01-20 14:29:00','2017-09-29 07:35:16',NULL,0),(229,'College website design  Menu menu website design  Mobile website design  Bookmark icon design  College homepage website design    Saint John Bosco College also told me that they were expecting to move into a brand new school, based in London Battersea, in September 2015. With the launch of this fantastic and exciting news and bringing together a brand new fresh online experience for visitors, and presence for their school and college, everything was fantastic. \r\n Interested in starting something together?\r\n\r\n I love meeting new people hearing what they want to achieve. Let\'s chat about what we can build together. \r\n\r\n Get started today \r\n ','SJBC College website design','I worked side-by-side with the head teacher and business manager at Saint John Bosco College, discussing and evaluating their previous website problems and issues. After overlooking their situation and uncovering exactly what they had visioned, I designed a complete bespoke website which was developed and integrated into a content management system (CMS), enabling there in-house team to make changes to the website data whenever and wherever they may be.','/case-studies/sjbc-college-website-design','2016-09-15 15:00:00','2017-10-23 14:26:15',NULL,0),(230,'Interested in starting something together?\r\n\r\n I love meeting new people hearing what they want to achieve. Let\'s chat about what we can build together. \r\n\r\n Get started today \r\n  Wood Street Capital are an independent UK based turnaround investor and private equity specialist focusing on financial investment and the provision of hands-on operational expertise to businesses facing stress, distress or other special situations. I received an email from a marketing manager in the middle of March 2014, asking for complete branding and website design for a new up