3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">24/7 Support Access, always reach for help</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Access support at almost any time through our fully integrated online ticketing system. Standard support operation times are 8am to 5pm, furthermore including live chat and an urgent priority for those naughty slip-ups.</p>\r\n'),(639,'<h3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">Full Management System (CMS), you&#39;ll have control</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I always have you at heart, things shouldn&#39;t be harder than they need to be. That&#39;s why I have put years of trust into our CMS. It&#39;s ease of use and broad functionality makes it a true winner for all our clients.</p>\r\n'),(640,'<h3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">Keep track with integrated Analytics and Reports</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As standard, I integrate Google Analytics (GA) into every website we develop. This allows you to view reports of visitor numbers, how visitors find you, referral websites, what visitors enjoy downloading and read on your website.</p>\r\n'),(641,'<h3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">Search Engine Optimisation (SEO), be crawled and found</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>All websites should be search engine friendly, because yours will be. Fully responsive, automatic creation of titles and meta tags, URL rewriting, search engine submission and speed optimisation.</p>\r\n'),(642,'<h3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">Reliable Hosting, in upward&nbsp;of a&nbsp;solid 99.9% uptime</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I have invested time and money in finding the fastest, safest and most reliable hosting around. I can promise all of this, as well as your website using the latest of technologies in it&rsquo;s class, with upward of 99.9% uptime.</p>\r\n'),(643,'<h3><strong class=\"colour-blue-dark\">Disaster Recovery for your data, we have you covered</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Your unique website will be hosted within our unique Azure virtual Infrastructure, which is ultra fast! This enabled me to take