rsquo;t, then I think you should make it one of your priorities to do so next year. But make sure you take clothes for all seasons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The footage I captured during our break, between the short and unexpected showers, were achieved with &ldquo;the sexiest drone that DJI ever designed&ldquo;, the <a href=\"https://www.dji.com/phantom-4\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"DJI Phantom 4\">DJI Phantom 4</a>. This was my first attempt in creating a trailer for anything, let alone a trailer of our short break. Yeh I could of improved it a lot and admittedly missed some opportunities to capture some unique footage, but this is how we learn. I look forward to creating something similar in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(1113,'<h3>Project goal</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.st-pauls.surrey.sch.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">St Pau&rsquo;s Catholic College</a> are an incredible group of talented individuals who have a passion to teach. With a proven track records of growing from strength to strength with every passing academic year, St Paul&rsquo;s was continuing to heighten themselves but unfortunately the their online expectation was merely frozen in time. Their website&rsquo;s in-house administration team were unable to swiftly update the content effortlessly on the original Microsoft SharePoint platform, and unable to enable parents, students and potential admissions to seamlessly visit and use their website on all possible devices. St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College understood that their website was falling behind and something needed to be done - quickly!</p>\r\n'),(1114,'<h3 id=\"focus-on-process-before-artifact\">Process&nbsp;and research&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Having previously been employed within the educational sector for 5 years, and now continuing to work alongside helping them for a further 4 years, I understand that brand consistency doesn&rsquo;t always transpire throughout a nursery, school, college or university. It was my job and passion to ensure that the brand of St Paul&rsquo;s continued throughout their newly <a href=\"{CCM:CID_212}\">designed responsive website</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The project began by ensuring I knew their previously outdated website and understanding their vision for improvement. We worked alongside the Network manager and leadership team at St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College to create a strategy aligned with their brand&rsquo;s ambition and audience&rsquo;s desires.</p>\r\n'),(1115,'<h3>Lessons Learned</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Since launching St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic college, we have seen an increase of mobile visitors through to their website. It&rsquo;s obviously that once parents, students and potential admissions become apparent of the responsiveness and mobile design enabling, more visitors feel comfortable viewing through their mobile devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The website has been live for approximately 5 months and the results are staggering on how much of an improvement a modern and responsive website has given. We&rsquo;ve split the 5 months down the middle and compared the two results to see how compatibility makes a difference.</p>\r\n'),(1116,'<h3>Testimonial</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>&ldquo;Thank you for the work you did with the redesign of our website, we have been getting very good feedback since its relaunch. Having a mobile enabled site with a fully integrated content management system is proving to be very useful, and also proving to be a key tool in communicating with our future, past and present pupils and parents. Once again, many thanks for your help and support throughout the entire process.&rdquo; - Network Manager</blockquote>\r\n'),(1117,'<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Providing such an individual and reliable web solution that supports the broad compatibilities which are truly needed within this day and age, has been an absolute pleasure. Collaboratively working alongside St Paul&rsquo;s Catholic College, has enabled me to effectively sling shot their online presence back into full swing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not have I provided the design and development their website solution, but also the continued hosting and monitoring of the solution. This again has provided fantastic results, such as a website uptime of 99.9%, with the average response rate of 359ms showing for the course of 5 months, since launch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No doubt, there will also be a guaranteed continuation of fantastic results to come in the near future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(1119,'<h3>Testimonial</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>&ldquo;Thank you for the work you did with the redesign of our website, we have been getting very good feedback since its relaunch. Having a mobile enabled site with a fully integrated content management system is proving to be very useful, and also proving to be a key tool in communicating with our future, past and present pupils and parents. Once again, many thanks for your help and support throughout the entire process.&rdquo; - Network Manager</blockquote>\r\n'),(1120,'<center>\r\n<h2><strong>Desktop Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>8,342</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>12,262</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>46.99%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n'),(1121,'<center>\r\n<h2><strong>Mobile Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>4,161</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>8,813</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>111.80%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n'),(1122,'<center>\r\n<h2><strong>Tablet Sessions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>first half - <strong>1,010</strong><br />\r\nseconds half - <strong>2,274</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>121.15%</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding-top:0;margin-top:0;\"><strong>Improvement</strong></p>\r\n</center>\r\n'),(1123,'<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Providing such an individual and reliable web solution that supports the broad compatibilities which are truly needed within this day and age, has be